description: Argo Gold Inc., a development stage company, focuses on the exploration and development of mineral properties in northwestern Ontario. The company explores for gold, silver, cobalt, and zinc deposits. Its flagship project is the 100% owned Uchi gold project covering 22 square kilometers located to the west of Uchi Lake in the Birch-Uchi Greenstone Belt, Ontario; and the 100% owned Talbot Lake gold project covering 760 hectares located in the Uchi geological sub-province. The company was formerly known as Arbitrage Exploration Inc. and changed its name to Argo Gold Inc. in September 2016. Argo Gold Inc. was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Ms. Judith E. Baker BSC, MBA
